Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful on your way home,\NInoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Is it near?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, so many false alarms…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, simply put,\Nwe're on special assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special assignment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows used for\Nexperiments got away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while being transported\Nunder escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them seems to have\Nsnuck into the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were given\Nthe special assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of finding and\Ncapturing the Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they leave\Nthat to us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a Hollow\Nundergoing experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the higher ups ordered us to\Ncapture it unharmed, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be counting on\Nyour help for a while, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? …How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know…\Nput us up for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you guys think you are,\Ndropping in out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide on things yourself\Nwhen I'm not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are,\Ndropping in out of the blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the gall\Nto talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is now Sis and my love nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Can you manage, Ichigo?\N– Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of squished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my place doesn't have\Nthe room to put the two of you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place,\Nyou once said you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"had no intention of\Nasking me any favors."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's with the sudden\Nchange of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, you can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:40.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,OUT INDEFINITELY\NTHE OWNER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like no one's in…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud,\Nwhere'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anyone else\Nyou can ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that we don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this case,\Ndo we have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put up\Nthese two again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, look after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this, nonchalant, "Can\Nyou pass the soy sauce" attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you looked after\Nthese two before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll manage somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk as if it's\Nnot your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.\NBe good to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you'll\Nget along just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "getting along"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a threat no matter\Nhow you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The baldhead itself is a threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bald, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, that's right…Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keigo! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making too much noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll annoy the neighbors if you\Nmake a ruckus by the front door…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home…Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say\N"welcome home"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you treating him\Nlike family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the front door open\Nall this time waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you lie like that\Nwithout a second thought?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you playing\Nthe devoted wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind not interrupting\Nour fateful reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I want to\Nbreak up that fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you\Naccept him so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what fate awaits us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept this hurt and lost\Nman without asking for a reason…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of woman\NI want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't care\Na rat's ass about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what type of\Nwoman you want to become!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you already said that\Nto him before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I love shaved heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not shaven,\Nhe's bald, I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, I'm not bald!\NGot that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of that banter…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are a loud bunch…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't\Nwant to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be out most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and though this is\Na special assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll finish in about a week,\NI'm sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last time, he went\Nback home before I knew it…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time I have to\Ncapture his heart for sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while he's still at our place…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To do that, I…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made it just for you…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your wallet, cell phone,\Nhandkerchief,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}keys and your train pass.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you have a bath first,\Nor dinner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have both ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are such a thoughtful woman…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't live without you…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darling…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it my "Operation: Thoughtful\NWoman Turns Her Man into Putty."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flawless! It's Flawless, Mizuho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a good breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakiniku in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat this in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.48,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WHOLE SHARK'S FIN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TENGU POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to engage\N	in this early in the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent Collagen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat so willingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These trotters are\Npretty good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,\Nwhere'd our clothes go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clothes you\Nhad on yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took those to the cleaners…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you, Ikkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're liking this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold it against me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I look great\Nin anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have these, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't wearing any of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is really messing me up…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as\Nwe're staying there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get this\Nover with quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and return to the Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's telling us the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far are you going to\Nkeep following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash your back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything crazy again,\NI'll kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be nice…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that woman's behavior\Nescalates any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have no choice\Nbut to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have somewhere to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be without\Na place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to think of some\Nsort of countermeasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the mission\Nis the least of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about? I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, look…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, but I love shaved heads.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you wear a wig,\Nher interest in you will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wear something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know till you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks great on you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit you are enjoying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No…not at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it for your sake, Ikkaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that looks about right,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought,\Nno way I'm wearing this thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes off easily,\Nit'll give it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.70,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SUPER EXTRA STRENGTH GLUE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I glued it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Yumichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna\Ndo about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you, Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, watch where\Nyou're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell were you looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at,\Ndammit…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing too much,\Nbastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what should I say,\Nit's just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it looks unexpectedly\Ngood on you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not convincing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nhow's your mission going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so far…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for\Nits Spiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we haven't found a trace …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, don't you have it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asking for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste my time\Ntalking to you guys! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So that was Ikkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She only realized that now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, you must be hungry…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Huh?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better take it off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have hair…why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for me to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yumichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being mean,\Ntreating me the same way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– It ain't right!\N– It's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly…\Nhow long are you people staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you out of here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beyond effective!\NWhy does it turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too troublesome to explain…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it means she has absolutely\Nno interest in you with hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the meaning\Nof my existence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in my shaven head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decline this place from my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never taking off the wig\Nwhen I'm in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember a man who'd\Ngrow out his hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it meant breaking\Na woman's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis…are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…\NI love shaved heads…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah…we're sleeping outside,\Nafter all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way is less stressful\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like getting\Nsome juice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you really ought to\Nbe more honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I just wanted juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Keigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's the one\Nwe're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird\Nattacked Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you waiting for?\NWe have a mission to do, Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This glue says it adheres the Gigai\Nand Konpaku to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just have to\Nwill my way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks for letting us stay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you come this way again,\Nyou can stay at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I will then …
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do something\Nabout that hair, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit nagging me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you all laughing,\Ndammit! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rusts, you can never\Nstab with it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grasp it incorrectly,\Nand it will rip you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you see,\Npride resembles a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In today's segment, we'll cover\NMayuri Kurotsuchi's Ashisogijizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claw out, Ashisogijizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashisogijizo has the power\Nto take away the movement
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the four limbs of\Nthe adversary it slashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike paralysis, the feeling\Nof pain remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Bankai form is\NKonjiki Ashisogijizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scatters a lethal poison\Nover a wide area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…that's a fine explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you candy as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apple-flavored poison candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,